main event: A UFO sighting involving multiple witnesses in Annapolis, Maryland, where a bright light was observed moving rapidly across the sky.
interesting points: The observed light was round and bright white, flashing on and off, The sighting lasted for approximately 3-4 minutes, Witnesses included a student from Annapolis as well as military police, Highly detailed reports indicated the objects were saucer-shaped, reddish-silver, and hovering, Residents reported excitement and alarm, prompting police and fire department calls.
sighted object: bright flashing light and saucer-shaped objects
witness description: students and military police in the area
